# Bhatti Agri-tech Frontend Style Guide

## Design System Overview

This project uses a modern design system built on:
- **Framework**: React 19 + TypeScript + Vite
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 with OKLCH color space
- **Component Library**: shadcn/ui (New York style)
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Router**: TanStack Router

---

## Domain Terminology

- **Dispatch / Nikasi**: "Dispatch" is the user-facing label for the **nikasi** gate-pass type. In code, use the `nikasi` identifier (e.g. `nikasiPasses`, `totalBagsNikasi`, gate pass type `'nikasi'`). In UI headers and labels, use "Dispatch" when showing nikasi totals or filters.

