## Typography

### Font Family
- **Primary Font**: Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Weights Available**: 300, 400, 500, 600, 700, 800, 900
- **Custom Class**: Always use `font-custom` class for Inter font family

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
<h1 className="font-custom text-4xl font-bold">Heading</h1>
<p className="font-custom text-base">Body text</p>

// ❌ BAD
<h1 className="text-4xl font-bold">Heading</h1> // Missing font-custom
```

### Font Weights by Element

| Element | Weight | Usage |
|---------|--------|-------|
| h1, h2 | 700 (font-bold) | Main headings |
| h3-h6 | 600 (font-semibold) | Subheadings |
| Body text | 400 (font-normal) | Default paragraphs |
| Buttons (default) | 500 (font-medium) | Standard buttons |
| Buttons (bold) | 700 (font-bold) | Primary CTAs |
| Table numbers | 500 (font-medium) | Data display |

### Typography Scale

```tsx
// Headings
<h1 className="font-custom text-[2.1rem] font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.5px] xl:text-[3rem]">
<h2 className="font-custom text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter lg:text-5xl">
<h3 className="font-custom text-2xl font-semibold lg:text-3xl">

// Body Text
<p className="font-custom text-base font-normal leading-[1.6] md:text-xl">
<p className="font-custom text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
```

