## Accessibility

### Required Patterns

1. **Focus States**: Always include `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary`
2. **ARIA Labels**: Use for icon-only buttons
3. **Semantic HTML**: Use proper heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)
4. **Alt Text**: Always provide for images
5. **Link Text**: Descriptive, not "click here"

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
<button aria-label="Close menu">
  <XIcon />
</button>

<img src="/logo.webp" alt="Coldop Logo" />

// ❌ BAD
<button><XIcon /></button> // Missing aria-label
<img src="/logo.webp" /> // Missing alt
```

